messages.message:
Would AI Hub hypothetically be able to tell which page an information came from or how many pages the uploaded document has (for example by getting the information from the underlying ibdoc/ibmsg)? Currently AI Hub usually tells us that '`it is not possible to determine the page because (... some reason)` .

Asking because the information could help with split-classification during a PoV.
short answer is no right now; this can be extended. btw is this document really an email?

It's a PDF where page 1 used to be an e-mail, page 2,3,4 are regular PDF pages then.

Best course of action is to create a PFR I assume :slightly_smiling_face:
This has come up a few times, i’ve seen customers ask things about which page things are on and are surprised its not able to answer that yet
These kind of questions will work in the multi-step converse
